        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <div class="faq-item">
            <h5>How do I book a ride?</h5>
            <p>Open the Cabocab customer app, enter your destination, choose the type of ride, and confirm your booking.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
            <h5>Can I schedule a ride in advance?</h5>
            <p>Yes, you can schedule a ride by selecting the “Schedule” option while booking, and setting your preferred date and time.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
            <h5>How can I track my ride in real-time?</h5>
            <p>Once your ride is confirmed, you can track your driver’s location in real-time on the map.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
            <h5>What payment methods are accepted in the app?</h5>
            <p>Payments are made directly to drivers. You can use cash or other accepted methods.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
            <h5>How do I rate my driver after a trip?</h5>
            <p>After the trip ends, you’ll be prompted to rate the driver based on your experience.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
            <h5>What safety features are available in the customer app?</h5>
            <p>You can use the in-app SOS button for emergencies, rate your driver, and access 24/7 customer support.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
            <h5>How can I contact customer support if there is an issue?</h5>
            <p>Use the “Help & Support” section in the app to reach our 24/7 customer service team.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

